   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## ✅ Résumé\n",
    "\n",
    "Votre pipeline nnUNetv2 est prêt. Étapes suivantes :\n",
    "\n",
    "```bash\n",
    "# Preprocessing\n",
    "nnUNetv2_plan_and_preprocess -d DATASET_ID --verify_dataset_integrity\n",
    "\n",
    "# Entraînement\n",
    "nnUNetv2_train DATASET_ID 3d_fullres 0\n",
    "\n",
    "# Inférence\n",
    "nnUNetv2_predict -i INPUT_FOLDER -o OUTPUT_FOLDER -d DATASET_ID -c 3d_fullres\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "📖 Documentation complète : https://github.com/MIC-DKFZ/nnUNet"
   ]
  }
 ]
